metadata.name: Fear City Comics Presents | Thumper #1
metadata.description:
Welcome to the world of Fear City. Your favorite character, Thumper is finally brought to life as you explore his origin story in the first of six volumes brought to you by Fear City Comics.

Head over to www.fearcity.io/thumper-comic-nft to read the full 24 page comic. Prepare yourself for the Comic NFT Burn Event in mid-2023 to receive your physical comic signed by Stephen Bliss.
